import { Button,Form } from 'react-bootstrap';
import React from 'react'



 const AddFormat = () => {
  return (
<Form className=''>
    <Form.Group>
        <Form.Control
        style={{margin:'10px'}}
            type="text"
            placeholder="Name *"
            required />
    </Form.Group>

    <Form.Group>
        <Form.Control
        style={{margin:'10px'}}
            type="email"
            placeholder="Email *"
            required />
    </Form.Group>

    <Form.Group>
        <Form.Control
        style={{margin:'10px'}}
            as="textarea"
            placeholder="Address"
            rows={3} />
    </Form.Group>

    <Form.Group>
        <Form.Control
        style={{margin:'10px'}}
            type="text"
            placeholder="phone"
             />
    </Form.Group>

    <Button variant="outline-success" type="submit" block>
        Add New Employee
    </Button>
 </Form>
  )
}
export default AddFormat;
